th Publishing Tools</strong>","If you are the type of person that writes reports, articles, blogs, faxes and more, then you need writing software that can speed up the publishing process. For example, <a href=\"https://www.laptopmag.com/articles/best-microsoft-office-alternatives\">StarOffice Writer</a> has tools that help you publish your text as HTML, PDF, a blog or as a wiki.","There&#39;s no need to switch back and forth between windows while you copy and paste text. In fact, you can even edit your wikis using this software.","<strong>Eliminate Graphics Software</strong>","Without the right word processing software, you will need separate graphic creating software such as Photoshop or Corel Draw to produce drawings to add to documents. And while you won&#39;t be professionally editing photos with simple word processors, you can do quite a bit with them. Writing software such as <a href=\"https://www.laptopmag.com/articles/best-microsoft-office-alternatives\">TextMaker</a> and <a href=\"https://www.laptopmag.com/articles/best-microsoft-office-alternatives\">Ragtime</a> have drawing tools built into the software, so you never have to leave your document to add a drawing. These types of software also have shapes, clipart and photos that you can add to your document with a few clicks of the button. No need to go scrounging up the right image on the internet.","<strong>Make Working with Collaborators Easy</strong>","In a work environment, you often need co-workers to collaborate on a document before it can be approved. This can mean a lot of printing and sticky notes, which take a lot of time to produce.<br/><br/>"]},"id":"8b7b6dec-95fe-4a08-ad30-6930354ec495","type":"text"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Getting your text documents finished faster, with better results, can give you more free time and, really, who doesn&#39;t want that?","To see how the best <a href=\"https://www.laptopmag.com/articles/best-microsoft-office-alternatives\">word processing programs</a> compar